Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  我来帮她换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才爱理来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说已经联系上了学姐的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱乃去休息吧  剩下的事交给我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽学姐  你太勉强自己了
